stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft: Commissioner creates election
    Draft --> Configured: Add levels + positions + candidates

    Configured --> Scheduled: Set start/end dates

    Scheduled --> Active: Activate (tokens become issuable)
    Active --> VotingOpen: Voting window begins

    VotingOpen --> Closed: Reaches end_date or manual close
    Active --> Closed: Force closed by commissioner

    Closed --> ResultsReady: Results computed internally

    ResultsReady --> Published: results_published = true
    Published --> Archived: PDF report generated & stored

    Archived --> [*]

    note right of Active
        - Voters can cast votes using tokens
        - Results remain sealed for everyone
        - Monitors see only turnout
    end note

    note right of Published
        - Full vote counts visible to all
        - Downloadable PDF report
        - Cannot be unpublished
    end note
